// Function action airline ticket management 
	Class AirlineTicket 
	// Aribute String 
	- codeFlight 
	- nameFlight 
	- dateTakeOff
	- baggageSign
	
	// Aritbute int
	- priceTicket
	
	* codeFlight entered format rules : 
	VJABB : VietJet, A from 0 -> 9, BB from 0 -> 9 
	VNABBC : VietnamAirlin, A from 0 -> 9, BB from 0 -> 9
	JETABB : JetStar, A from 0 -> 9, BB from 0 -> 9 

- 1. Enter infor n flight with code flight (format)
- 2. Save information flight entered on text file (DataFlight.txt)
- 3. Read information flight on file (DataFlight.txt) and show on screen 
- 4. Show information after sort data format decrease price ticket
- 5. Print information each flight on file respectively (example: infor flight 1 save on file flight_1.txt );   



